What you need to know:

The French can boast two wins over the triple world champions at the tournament - 43-31 in the 1999 semi-finals and 20-18 in the last eight in 2007.Both games are regarded as modern classics.In total, the 2023 World Cup features 48 matches and nine host cities -- Paris, Marseille, Nice, Lille, Toulouse, Lyon, Bordeaux, Saint-Etienne and Nantes.